{"tid":1425152,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你班廢老咪再用外國勢力嚟打飛機！","createTime":"2019-08-06T17:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:36:55.000Z","uid":196677,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"438c8c8d0c03c4347138c1c54034dea669903c87","tid":1425152,"uid":196677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:17:36.000Z","msg":"你班廢老成日話外國勢力<br />\n根本就係因為你地太自視過高<br />\n你地唔容許班後生聰明，識諗，有組織力，有超強嘅學習力<br />\n你地唔願意相信長江後浪推前浪<br />\n你地唔願意相信你地𠴱套已經過時<br />\n你地唔願意相信成個社會都進步緊唯獨係你地原地踏步<br />\n你地唔願意相信你地做唔到/唔敢做嘅野竟然比班後生做到<br />\n<br />\n你地淨係識得用想當年嚟打飛機<br />\n而家就而家咪再喺度想當年<br />\n想當年你點捱點剩都好我地全部香港人而家都係生存喺同一個時空<br />\n唔好再同我講食鹽多過你食米因為而家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好多後生食蛋都多過你食米！</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我淨係知你口中所謂嘅關心香港只係關心緊你自己嘅香港<br />\n而我地  係關心大家嘅香港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人加油</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef157b6ecbdd389d65e04a4566ffcceb8971583","tid":1425152,"uid":259700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:24:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81c2173693b947b168e6908a408a45e9f2ace4f0","tid":1425152,"uid":162046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ef157b6ecbdd389d65e04a4566ffcceb8971583","tid":1425152,"uid":259700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:24:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:36:55.000Z","msg":"Hi 藍友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過歡迎比老人家睇下話佢知唔關美國事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}